description.1: Beast has got a busy day ahead of him. With a hot date planned for the evening and a training session with the mutant Beak during the day, what could go wrong?
description.2: The vampiric, primal Anzati, under the leadership of Volfe Karkko, have overrun the prison planet of Kiffex. All lives on the planet are threatened as Karkko sends his followers out to collect beings to feed his hunger. Three Jedi Knights stranded on this planet make a stand against both a cantina full of enraged prisoners and a band of Anzati hunters led by Aayla, a former Padawan of Quinlan Vos. Quin, already struggling with the draw of the dark side, fights alongside Jedi Masters Tholme and Zao, and the ever-scheming Devaronian, Villie. After a surprising confrontation with Aayla, Quin and his companions are joined by another mysterious Jedi and find themselves victims of a conspiracy but are the last hope for hundreds of prisoners on Kiffex... and possibly the entire galaxy!'
description.3: In an altered'Star Wars'timeline, the'Death Star'is never destroyed and theRebellion'is seemingly crushed. The'Empire's strong presence throughoutthe galaxy'leads to the formation of a new'Senate, filled with Imperial puppets.'Han Solo'and'Chewbacca'watch in amazement as the newest Senator'from the planet'Coruscant, the Imperial Throneworld, is announced -'Leia Organa! Hope springs on'Dagobah, as'Luke Skywalker'nears the completion of his training with'Jedi Master'Yoda. But can any amount of training prepare him for the combined dark forces of the'Emperor,'Darth Vader, and Leia, Vader's new apprentice?
description.4: The war'on'Ruusan'between the'Jedi'Army of Light'and the'Sith Brotherhood of Darkness'all comes down to one event, an event'that sends shockwaves across'the galaxy'and will forever change the relationship between'good'and'evil.'A devastating weapon of mass destruction'will have a deadly effect on the'planet, leaving those left living wishing they had perished with their comrades. Who shall live to see another day, and who will vanish into history?
description.5: If young'Anakin Skywalker'is to become a'Jedi'he must follow the teachings of his'Master,'Obi-Wan Kenobi. He must also find a way to overcome his fears, including the memory of the vicious Darth Maul, the man who killed his friend Qui-Gon Jinn.
description.6: It's Survivor - Punisher style! Trapped on the remote scrap of dirt known as Grand Nixon Island, it's the Punisher vs. an army of psychotic mercenary criminals! Will Frank Castle make it off alive?
description.7: To complete their mission, The Exiles must track down Forge. Plus, the Exiles do battle with Professor Xavier himself!
description.11: On the anniversary of Uncle Ben's death, the web-slinger heads where he always does: the Ballpark. There he'll reminisce about the man whose words formed the mantra of his life, and about the day when fate dropped out of the sky and landed on young Peter Parker's head... literally!
description.13: The UNIVERSE X spotlight swings on the Master of Magnetism! On a planet where everyone is a mutant, can Magneto be a hero?
description.14: What is the Man-Ape's plan for T'Challa? And why is Everett K. Ross paid a pleasant visit by Henry Peter Gyrich?
description.15: Captain America and Agent 13 attempt to gather intel on the helicarrier that Red Skull stole. Plus, Fury resumes command as the Director of SHIELD!
description.16: CAUGHT IN BETWEEN! A gang war between Kingpin and Canis heats up, and Spider-Girl just can't seem to remove herself from being in the middle!
description.17: Chamber begins to have doubts about his brush with fame and his relationship with Sugar Kane. Mr. Clean talks with the Church of Humanity.
description.18: Wolverine is thrown back into the Weapon X Project, where he is flooded with all his old, twisted memories.
description.19: What's it like to work for the Kingpin? Even scarier and more dangerous than you might think!
description.20: Pyslocke has been slain and Beast is on death's door. Can the X-Men avenge Betsy's death? Plus, Tessa uses a never-before-seen power!
description.22: Turmoil strikes the heart of the Fantastic Four! Johnny's flame powers have gone haywire, and he can't flame off anymore! That kind of life is something Ben Grimm knows a thing or two about - so why is he quitting the team?
description.23: When a rich man decides to sue Daredevil for property damage, he hires Matt Murdock as his attorney. Wait a minute, Matt Murdock is Daredevil! So how can the Man Without Fear be in two places at once? Plus, a very special back-up tale that guest-stars Spider-Man, penciled by legendary DD artist Gene Colan, and scripted by none other than Stan Lee!
description.25: SPIDER-MAN & THE PUNISHER PART 1 The Punisher has escaped from Ryker's Island! Spider-Man is on the scene!
description.27: X-Force travels to Bastrona to rescue Paco Perez, a mutant hostage!
description.29: What would you do if you knew you were a ticking time bomb? Brian Azzarello (100 Bullets) and Richard Corben (House on the Borderland) have a startling answer! Doc Samson's got Bruce Banner, and his monstrous alter ego, just where he wants him!
description.32: Flaming skulls! Burning chrome! High adventure and extreme vengeance! Ghost Rider is back, and Johnny Blaze isn't happy! Sure, turning into a demonic biker was fun at first, but now Johnny's alter-ego is getting out of control! And as the bodies pile up, Johnny comes to a hard decision, one that may mean his death!
description.34: There are two Hank Pyms and they are both on death's door! The only person that can save them is...Triathlon?
description.42: Kang finishes up the preparations for his assault on planet Earth! Meanwhile, the Vision infiltrates the enigmatic Triune Understanding.
description.43: The new Weapon X recruits Deadpool. In return, he gets that beautiful face of his back!
description.44: E For Extinction Part 3 (of 3)  The X-Men are the only force capable of taking down the manical Cassandra Nova.  Plus, has the White Queen joined the X-Men?  And Xavier makes a shocking decision!
description.45: Bad things are happening on the prison planet of Kiffex. A Guardian outpost on the planet has been overrun by the vampiric Anzati and weapons from the outpost have spread to the inmates. When Jedi Quinlan Vos, a direct descendant of the Guardians, is summoned to help investigate the disaster, he cannot refuse. But the Jedi, who is struggling with the draw of the dark side, may be in for more than he bargained. Fortunately, Quin has the help of his scheming Devaronian pal Villie, his former Master, Tholme, and unexpected support in the shape of a small blind cook. Quin will need all the help he can get to survive this mission and avoid falling into the darkness!
description.47: The devastated planet of'Ruusan'has endured much during the war between the'Jedi'Army of Light'and the'Sith'Brotherhood of Darkness. Its forests have been decimated and its inhabitants mercilessly slaughtered. The war is not over yet and many more will suffer before it ends. Of three young cousins sent to Ruusan, one will willfully join with the dark, one will seek out the light, and one will fulfill a destiny that none could have possibly foreseen.'
description.50: Frank Castle is headed for the South Pacific for his kind of fun in the sun! The Punisher is tracking an international cartel that's resurrected an old enemy! What will the one-man-army do on an island full of mercenaries, criminals and psychos?
description.53: SPIDER-MAN & IRON MAN PART 2 The mysterious partner to the Latverian attackers is unveiled. Plus, Tony Stark's past is revealed!
description.55: Scandal continues to surround X-Force when new and old members are shuffled around and go head to head! Meanwhile U-Go Girl throws a tantrum over the announcement of the team's new leader.
description.57: Having located the green-skinned monstrosity in the New Mexico desert, Doc Samson prepares his troops for a High Noon showdown. With a 1,000 Blackhawk helicopters at his disposal, the mysterious government agent has a formidable arsenal, but he's brought along a secret weapon -- just to be safe!
description.59: Get out your leather and fire up that hog, because the original Ghost Rider is tearing up the highway once again, and he's badder and wilder than ever! A flaming skull. A cold metal chain. A revved-up Harley. It's been a long time since Johnny Blaze lived the life of the Ghost Rider. Now he's back, and roaring off on his most insane adventure yet! But this is a wilder, more uncontrollable Spirit of Vengeance than he's ever experienced! So if Johnny wants to live life in the fast lane, he might also end up splattered all over it as roadkill!
description.61: Fusion has the power to break Spider-Man's neck like a toothpick. The question remains...what is inspiring this mad man?!
description.63: SEDUCTION OF THE INNOCENT PART 3 T'Challa is faced with an impossible choice: marry the killer known as Malice, or murder her to prevent a tribal war in Wakanda! And what about Malice's victims? Who lives? Find out in the third chapter of "Seduction of the Innocent!"
description.64: Now that Connie knows Cap's secret, can she go on loving him?
description.65: A stalker, a mysterious Spider-Man, and a new underworld figure...what else could go wrong for May Parker?
description.66: The X-Men battle Mr. Clean. Chamber tries to cope with his fifteen minutes of fame.
description.67: As if things couldn't get worse, Wolverine becomes the snack of the vampire Mauvais! Meanwhile, Peepers comes to Beast's rescue.
description.68: The bizarre creature known as the Thousand has finally revealed his true face to Spidey...and now it's time for one of the most gruesome rumbles you've ever seen!
description.81: Includes four different X-Men adventures! Featuring: Dazzler, Nightcrawler, Magik, and the space pirate Starjammers!
description.82: The saga of Quinlan Vos, a troubled Jedi still trying to regain stability after having his memory erased, continues in this latest Star Wars story arc. Despite his successful mission on Dathomir, the Jedi Council still feels that he walks dangerously close to the dark side. Kiffex, a prison planet under watch by the Guardians, is suddenly thrust into chaos when an unidentified enemy decimates a security compound. Quinlan Vos is specifically requested to investigate because of his Guardian ancestry, and he soon finds himself on another suicide mission.
description.85: The war between'Jedi'and'Sith'continues to rage on the planet of'Ruusan, consuming all in its path. The battle between good and evil has claimed soldiers on both sides and now the rage boils over and starts to consume the planet itself. Ruusan's forests and countryside become victims of the war along with innocent bystanders and the native creatures called Bouncers'which occupy the sky above the planet. In the midst of the firestorm, cousins'Tomcat'and'Bug'find it difficult to reach any common ground and continue to grow further apart. Meanwhile, their missing cousin Rain's'Force'powers grow as she struggles to find her way back to her family.
description.86: E For Extinction Part 2 (of 3)  Cassandra Nova stands responsible for the murder of 16 million mutants and the X-Men are bringing her down - dead or alive!
description.87: It's a real odd couple when the grim Frank Castle and the wise-cracking wall-crawler Spider-Man unite against an unstoppable human weapon!
description.93: SEDUCTION OF THE INNOCENT PART 2 People are dropping dead all over New York City, and Malice is to blame! And unless Black Panther gives himself fully to her she's going to kill everyone he's ever loved! All this, plus super sleuth Dakota North!
description.94: Cap frees himself from Crimson Dynamo, but can the Sentinel of Liberty take down Dynamo AND Ferrari.
description.95: SPIDER-GIRL IS BACK! May's powers have returned just in time to uncover the truth behind this new Spider-Man and the reappearance of a mysterious villain.
description.96: A new team lineup debuts as the X-Men become involved with an underground mutant colony in London.
description.97: While imprisoned at The Cage, Wolvie lands himself in solitary confinement, while X-Man Beast is assaulted.
description.98: The web-slinger is being pursued by a relentless foe who gives new meaning to the adage "beauty is only skin-deep"!
description.99: The biggest mystery in U.S. military history is about to be blown wide open, as the survivors and descendants of America's WWII superhumans finally discover the truth behind Operation: Firefly.

0.text: In order to save him, why must Ant-Man take a fantastic voyage inside the gamma-powered behemoth known as the Hulk? And will his cure prove worse than the certain death awaiting Bruce Banner?

9.text: Spider-Man unmasked!  Peter Parker confides to Mary Jane that he is actually Spider-Man...and things will never be the same!

10.text: Deadpool must not only contend with the villainous Street Speeder, but also with a jealous girlfriend! When Siryn comes calling on Deadpool, Copycat takes matters into her own hands!

12.text: The Silver Surfer is joined by the Iron Avengers, the Sentinels, and Magneto, to battle the Absorbing Man! Meanwhile, Peter Parker, Venom, and the New York heroes do what they can to stave off the end of the world

13.text: The UNIVERSE X spotlight swings on the Master of Magnetism! On a planet where everyone is a mutant, can Magneto be a hero?

Pyslocke has been slain and Beast is on death's door. Can the X-Men avenge Betsy's death? Plus, Tessa uses a never-before-seen power!

21.text: After 25 years, the third pod opens and it might spell the end of humankind. The Fixer stole Ogre’s identity…what revenge plot will Ogre hatch against Fixer?

25.text: SPIDER-MAN & THE PUNISHER PART 1 The Punisher has escaped from Ryker's Island! Spider-Man is on the scene!
SPIDER-MAN & THE PUNISHER PART 1 The Punisher has escaped from Ryker's Island! Spider-Man is on the scene!

26.text:
Black Widow and Dagger battle an army of death-dealing robots across the
S.H.I.E.L.D. Helicarrier, all under the command of the rogue AI known as
CELINE! Meanwhile, Punisher is determined to settle accounts with
Daredevil and forces the frightened Vermin to lead him to the hero!
Plus: Luke Cage and Shang-Chi get dinner!

Black Widow and Dagger battle an army of death-dealing robots across the S.H.I.E.L.D. Helicarrier, all under the command of the rogue AI known as CELINE! Meanwhile, Punisher is determined to settle accounts with Daredevil and forces the frightened Vermin to lead him to the hero!

30.text: A shadowy exchange is underway in China, one that involves the sale of a powerful mutant named Xorn. Wolverine and Domino undertake a daring mission to stop the sale and the destruction of China!
Who is John Sublime? What does he want with the ultra powerful mutant known as Xorn, detainee of Ao Jun prison? Cyclops intends to find out!

31.text: If you thought Iron Man hit his maximum cool factor, wait till you see his brand new armor!

33.text: More all-out international action with Marvel's sexiest assassin! It's war in Iraq over the mysterious artifact known as the Scorpio Key! And Elektra's right in the middle of it, battling for her life against a surprise enemy! Plus, the espionage agency known as S.H.I.E.L.D. has a new secret- and it may cost Nick Fury his life!

35.text: The Agent's thrill-a-minute limited series continues! Trapped between turmoil in Atlantis and political infighting within his own unit, U.S. Agent must cope with the mounting pressure as he fights his way to the source of the conspiracy swirling around him. Of course, it's when the pressure's the highest that the Agent is most apt to make a bull-headed mistake… and this one could prove fatal!

37.text: When Atlantean Beasts attack! The FF and Black Panther return to the Baxter Building to confront a coastal assault orchestrated by Namor! Meanwhile, the Human Torch and Crystal try to find a missing link to unlock the full potential of the Terrigen Mists.

39.text: The Shi'ar, the Skrulls, and the Kree have faced many great obstacles in their conquest of the future Earth, but even they're not prepared for the attack of the giant Captain Marvel ... Yes, we said GIANT Captain Marvel...

40.text: Daredevil continues his one-man campaign against the men responsible for his father's death! Plus, Matt's first meeting with Karen Page.

41.text: Phoenix joins Cable in their battle to prevent the Sisterhood from assuming control over the presidency of the United States!

44.text: E For Extinction Part 3 (of 3)  The X-Men are the only force capable of taking down the manical Cassandra Nova.  Plus, has the White Queen joined the X-Men?  And Xavier makes a shocking decision!

46.text: Bruce Banner is gone, now only the Hulk remains! The descent into darkness brings the Hulk face-to-face with an old enemy, one with the solution to all of the gamma goliath's problems -- that is, if he's willing to pay the terrible cost!

48.text: The Negative Zone epic ends here!

51.text: WAKE UP PART 4 Ben uncovers the truth behind the mystery of Leap Frog and his son!

52.text:
RETURN TO WEAPON X PART 1 (of 6)
The only mutant to ever make it outside the walls of Weapon X has been the Adamantium-clawed Wolverine...until now! Get a look inside the Ultimate Universe's Weapon X program and see what is in store for the mutants!

53.text: SPIDER-MAN & IRON MAN PART 2 The mysterious partner to the Latverian attackers is unveiled. Plus, Tony Stark's past is revealed!
SPIDER-MAN & IRON MAN PART 2 The mysterious partner to the Latverian attackers is unveiled. Plus, Tony Stark's past is revealed!

54.text:
Shang-Chi, master of kung-fu, is a hero - but his father is pure evil!
And when his dear daddy launches a major assault on the Knights, one
member calls it quits! But who leaves: Daredevil, Moon Knight, Luke
Cage...or Shang-Chi himself? Meanwhile, there's something rotten at the
heart of S.H.I.E.L.D. - and Dagger and Black Widow are determined to
find out what it is!

Shang-Chi, master of kung-fu, is a hero - but his father is pure evil! And when his dear daddy launches a major assault on the Knights, one member calls it quits! But who leaves: Daredevil, Moon Knight, Luke Cage...or Shang-Chi himself? Meanwhile, there's something rotten at the heart of S.H.I.E.L.D. - and Dagger and Black Widow are determined to find out what it is!

58.text: Iron Man is the bomb! No, literally...

60.text: The battle between Deadpool and Punisher rages on as the two clash all over the city!

62.text: Mephisto's grand plan stands revealed! Find out how and why he has been manipulating the minds of Thanos, Nighthawk, Gargoyle and Dr. Doom.

69.text: LEARNING CURVE PART 5.  Can Spidey escape the Kingpin, Electro and hordes of criminals with the evidence that Wilson Fisk is a murderer?  Or has Spider-Man gotten himself into more trouble than he can handle?

70.text: Rogue and Sage set out on a daring rescue mission! But to get to their teammates they will have to go through Vargas first!
Rogue and Sage set out on a daring rescue mission! But to get to their teammates they will have to go through Vargas first!

71.text: Charcoal, under an enormous amount of pressure, finally reaches a breaking point when his father returns as part of the Secret Empire!

72.text:
In trying to head off the horrible fate awaiting Marlo, Marv begins an odyssey into the future, where he immediately discovers he's the only being in the universe capable of saving the Earth from a conquering, power-hungry alliance of the Kree, Skrull and Shi'ar!
32 PGS./MARVEL PSR...$2.99

73.text: Yelena Belova, a young yet dangerous assassin, seeks to claim the mantle of Black Widow from Natasha Romanov, a former Soviet spy who defected to the West.

74.text: Heroes from across the timescape find themselves outside of time and reality. They are Blink, Nocturne, Magnus, Morph, Mimic, and Thunderbird. They have been brought there by the Time Broker. And they have one chance to save their dimensions.

Heroes from across the timescape find themselves outside of time and reality. They are Blink, Nocturne, Magnus, Morph, Mimic, and Thunderbird. They have been brought there by the Time Broker. And they have one chance to save their dimensions.

75.text: Irene learns the origins of the Sisterhood from Cable as they try to figure out the Dark Mother's next move.

77.text: Dr. Doom continues his quest for power! But what is his ultimate goal? And exactly how will the Inhumans play a part in helping him attain it?

78.text: The villain stands revealed in this series' shocking conclusion! Now, the only way to stop him lies with Iron Cross (whose last chance to atone for the sins of his people might require sacrificing all he believes in), the Mighty Destroyer (who is more interested in using the worldwide threat for his own goals than he is in stopping it), and Citizen V (whose actions reveal a shocking secret that will rock the V-Battalion, and the Thunderbolts)!

79.text: John Walker is back, and this time, he's the Commission's hand-picked operative in charge of superhuman incarceration! It's the chance he's been waiting for to get out from Captain America's shadow and kick bad guy butt! That is, if a deadly super-villain conspiracy, a woman from his past, and his own lousy attitude don't louse it all up!

83.text: Paul Jenkins' final story begins! The ravaged body of Bruce Banner quits, leaving the Hulk no other option but to turn to his greatest nemesis!

84.text: The jam-packed conclusion to THE HIDDEN YEARS! Will Magneto's war divide and conquer?! Or will the world find a brief period of peace and coexistence between mutant and human? Take a nostalgic trip through time to the X-Men’s most classic era!

86.text: E For Extinction Part 2 (of 3)  Cassandra Nova stands responsible for the murder of 16 million mutants and the X-Men are bringing her down - dead or alive!

89.text: Creel is whole! Now, the monster that destroyed the Avengers is back with a vengeance! Meanwhile, in the land of the dead, the heroes have made their way to Death, Thanos, and Mephisto.

91.text: LEARNING CURVE PART 4.  It's round 2 for Spider-Man as he takes the offensive against Electro and the Kingpin's Enforcers.  And if he succeeds, Spidey may get the evidence he needs to put the Kingpin away for good!

92.text: Deadpool is hired by the Gnucci crime family to kill the deadliest man in the Marvel U.  That's right, it's Deadpool vs. the Punisher!

99.text: The biggest mystery in U.S. military history is about to be blown wide open, as the survivors and descendants of America's WWII superhumans finally discover the truth behind Operation: Firefly.
The X-Men in an new X-Treme era! Storm, Bishop, Beast, Psylocke, and Thunderbird have been captured-will Sage be able to rescue them?
